//seekingalpha.com/symbol/TEAM\" title=\"Atlassian Corporation\">TEAM</a></span>) provides software that drives connection between teams, information, and workflows across the entire organization, including planning and project management, content creation and sharing and video collaborations. Atlassian has been expanding their product offerings over the past few</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/726778557/image_726778557.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743038-atlassian-growth-beyond-jira-and-confluence-initiate-with-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 18:21:03"}, {"id": "4743034", "title": "Enbridge, South Bow And The 25% Tariff On Canadian Imports To The US", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303200636/image_1303200636.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Tourists by Tower Bridge in snow\" data-id=\"1303200636\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1144px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303200636/image_1303200636.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303200636/image_1303200636.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303200636/image_1303200636.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303200636/image_1303200636.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303200636/image_1303200636.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303200636/image_1303200636.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303200636/image_1303200636.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303200636/image_1303200636.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Gary Yeowell/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>On November 25, President-elect Donald Trump announced his plans to impose 25% tariffs on imports from Canada and Mexico. Four days after the announcement, Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau went to Florida to meet with the future US</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303200636/image_1303200636.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743034-enbridge-south-bow-25-percent-tariff-on-canadian-imports-to-us", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 18:13:47"}, {"id": "4743030", "title": "Carlisle Companies: Trump's Policies, Industry Trends To Aid Earnings", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"3d kehystalo\" data-id=\"858503152\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"960px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Madmaxer/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Founded in 1917, <strong>Carlisle Companies Incorporated </strong>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CSL\" title=\"Carlisle Companies Incorporated\">CSL</a></span>) manufactures energy-efficient building solutions such as roofing products, insulation, waterproofing, and engineered HVAC products. The company has two segments, Construction Materials and Weatherproofing Technologies, with 75% and 25% of total revenues, respectively, </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743030-carlisle-companies-trump-policies-industry-trends-to-aid-earnings", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 18:05:47"}, {"id": "4743028", "title": "SNDL Shows Continued Improved Financials And Free Cash Flow For Q3-2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/1419163520/photo/macro-cannabis-flower-on-white-background.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=JI3HVVs661gHCZZ3cgYa-yDGARpoqz_B1GCmD9Kq6AU=\" alt=\"Macro Cannabis Flower on White Background\" data-id=\"1419163520\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">carlofranco/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>SNDL (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">